[comment]
Ford Crystler, big job for Junktown.

Needs you to talk to the Hub's Sheriff -> Gets you 300xp (can earn an extra 50xp if your barter skills are over 40)
After you come back you can sell bulk items to him, and accept a Junktown "job"

He buys bulk items, regardless of item it'll get you 500 xp and 500 caps.

12x 10mm Pistol, 44 Magnum, DEagle, Leather Armor
50x Junk or Wood or GunPowder
35x Metal Parts

Completing his Quest allows access to the Hub's even greater Bulk Order Jobs, which can't be done unless set up here.  

