{12000}{}{Well, I hate to break it to you, but you should just pack your bags, and head back East. There ain't nothing left here but death and poverty. I trust you know how to handle yourself out there?}
{12010}{}{Sure}
{12020}{}{Not really}
{13000}{}{[The man looks deep into your eyes] Yeah... I know that look. You best be on your best behavior inside my town, ya' hear? Now, I understand why a man needs to kill another man, but you don't go killin' no one in my town. Ya hear?! You drag that bastard outside, and do it there!}
