{25010}{}{So you want me to go over there and preach the good word of Junktown? }
{26000}{}{I need you to show him that both our cities can work together! We'll give them all the spare parts they need in exchange for 1/3 of their excess water and ammo. It's a pretty good deal, damnit! We might lose out on a bit of caps here and there, but they sure as hell won't be. Everytime we win a bid we take back a little more than half of their excess goods, just to sell it all right back to them a week later. It's a useless vicious cycle and all it has caused so far has been bureaucratic headaches and dead patrols.  }
{26010}{}{I'm not too good with words, I don't think he'll listen to me. }
{26020}{}{I get it now, politics are more than just caps. }
{26030}{}{Uh, okay.}
{27000}{}{*Sigh* It doesn't matter if he'll listen to you or not. I've been sending countless runners over to him. Eventually he will listen to reason, I'm not expecting you to work a miracle, I'm just expecting you to try. Just tell him that whatever past we had is over with, I forgive him, "politics is more than just caps".  }
{27010}{}{I'll go talk to him.}
{28000}{}{I'm glad you understand what I'm trying to tell you. We need to work together before we either kill each other, or starve to death. Tell him that I forgive him, and that our past has been wiped clean. I'm not expecting you to work a miracle here, I'm just expecting you to try.  }
{28010}{}{I'll go talk to him.}
{29000}{}{Hey there @pname@, any news?}
{29010}{}{I talked to Ford...}
{29020}{}{Still working on it.}
{30000}{}{Oh? And?}
{30010}{}{You didn't have to lie to me.}
{31000}{}{[The man laughs] Hah! Yeah but I needed to know if your heart was in the right place. Durango must have told you a bit of the details, we just need grunts to do the grunt work. It pays grunt pay but in the long run you'll be benefiting both yourself and the city you are working for. It's the little things here and there that make the biggest difference. }
{31010}{}{Well I'm looking for work, what do you have available? }
{32000}{}{We've got more or less the same deal going as the one you were offered in the Hub, our jobs are just easier. We mostly need resources from the mines, junk parts from the Boneyard, and wood from the surrounding areas. We do need some basic combat gear however. Leather armor, Desert Eagles, 44. Magnums, and 10mm Pistols are also in high demand. It's getting too expensive buying new gear from the Gun Runners every week so we are turning to the outside. Durango and I needed a way to scout out potential workers looking to make an honest buck. This is it @pname@.}
{32010}{}{I'll keep this in mind, thanks for the opportunity. }
{32020}{}{Let's talk about the combat gear you needed.}
{32030}{}{I'll think about it, goodbye.}
{33000}{}{It's labour there's really not too much to say about it. Grab a sledgehammer head over to the mines and start producing Metal Parts or Gunpowder. I'll buy batches of 35x Metal Parts and batches of 50x boxes of Gunpowder. If your not into mining for a living you can chop down some trees or collect Kunk over in the Boneyard. I'll pay you for every 50x pieces of Kunk you bring me, or 50x pieces of Wood you collect.  }
{33010}{}{You mentioned something about armor and weapons?}
{33020}{}{Sounds good. }
{34000}{}{I need lots of basic weaponry, we're talking crates of 10mm pistols, .44 magnums, or Desert Eagles. A dozen of any of those guns will get you a good price around here, either with me or Killian. Trade them to whoever you want but just remember that I'm the only guy that can guarantee you'll get caps.  }
{34010}{}{You mentioned something about a mining job?}
{34020}{}{Sounds good. }
{35000}{}{Hey @pname@, what's the news? Got any crates to sell?}
{35010}{}{Tell me about mining for Junktown.}
{35020}{}{Let's talk about the combat gear you needed.}
{35030}{}{Yeah, let's trade.}
{35040}{}{No, not today.}
{36000}{}{Feels good to do some real work for a change, doesn't it? What do you have, @pname@?}
{36010}{}{12x 10mm Pistols}
{36020}{}{12x .44 Magnums.}
{36030}{}{12x Desert Eagles.}
{36040}{}{12x Leather Armor.}
{36050}{}{35x Metal Parts.}
{36060}{}{50x Boxes of Gunpowder.}
{36070}{}{50x Pieces of Junk.}
{36080}{}{50x Pieces of Wood.}
{36090}{}{Nothing actually, I'll be back.}
{37000}{}{Let's have a look here... Everything seems to be in order. You've done some good things for Junktown, and we appreciate it. Here's 500 caps, @pname@. Keep these crates coming, and you'll always be welcome in Junktown. }
{37010}{}{I've got some more crates to sell.}
{37020}{}{Thanks for the caps, see you around.}

